Namespace Prefixes

ns_prefix.Rd

Prefixes for namespaces, primarily sourced from ROBOT, that cover most uses in OBO Foundry ontologies, with slight modification to match the prefixes as used in the Human Disease Ontology and a few additional prefixes for cross-references and DO-related SPARQL query support.

Usage

ns_prefix

obo_prefix

obo_prop_prefix

not_obo_prefix

Format

Character vectors of namespaces named by their corresponding prefix:

ns_prefix: Superset of all 533 objects listed below.

obo_prefix: 255 standard OBO Foundry namespaces (e.g. AAO = "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/AAO_").

obo_prop_prefix: 255 OBO Foundry property namespaces; these may not all be in actual use (e.g. aao = "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/aao#")

not_obo_prefix: 21 namespaces outside but commonly used in the OBO Foundry (e.g. dc = "http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"), or in federated SPARQL queries with the DO (e.g. up = "http://purl.uniprot.org/core/").

Source

ROBOT (v1.9.4) via data-raw/ns_prefix.R; last updated 2023-06-12.
